title: Spoof video sees Trump threaten to build a wall between Devon and Cornwall
text:
A spoof video of Donald Trump threatening to build a wall between Devon and Cornwall has gone viral. The clip, voived by Tony Goodman from Fowey has ben viewed on the internet over a million times.
In the tongue-in-cheek clip the US President is seen to threaten to start building the wall at Bude and on the Tamar Bridge.
